title: A College Hockey Feast!
description: 5 Minnesota teams in the NCAA hockey tournament, and #92Noon had all five coaches on the Thursday show before it begins! SCSU's Brett Larson, Gophers' Bob Motzko, Mankato's Mike Hastings, Bemidji's Tom Serratore and UMD's Scott Sandelin!
